ChatGPT
When you see the status "modified: HP (new commits, modified content, untracked content)", it indicates that the branch or folder HP has the following:

New commits: Changes have been committed locally but not yet pushed to the remote repository.
Modified content: Some tracked files in the HP branch/folder have been changed but not yet committed.
Untracked content: There are new files or directories not added to Git tracking yet.
Here’s how you can handle this step by step:

1. Check the Status

